--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.1 (2020-11-27)
B: Update path to systemctl binary
E: Improve Monit configuration file

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-11-27)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (openssh_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.3.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 0.3.1 (2020-02-24)
E: Use Ansible module copy instead of template for static moduli file

* Version 0.3.0 (2019-11-13)
C: Add support for Debian 10
C: Drop support for Debian 9

* Version 0.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 0.1.1 (2019-04-15)
E: Allow additional message authentication codes (OpenSSH client)

* Version 0.1.0 (2019-01-07)
F: Initial release
